uu-app-binarystore/createBinary
resources.description:
#### uuCmd documentation
https://uuapp.plus4u.net/uu-bookkit-maing01/34df77ebe0a04adda6dcd62d32c4f513/book/page?code=createBinary_00

#### Input
```javascript
{
  code: "...", //externally specified or generated code (3-64 charecters)
  name: "...", //user name of binary; It is uu5String limited to 255 characters
  description: "...", //user description of binary; It is uu5String limited to 4000 characters
  versionName: "...", //user name of binary version; It is uu5String limited to 255 characters
  filename: "..." //name of the uploaded file; 
                  //if not set it is obtained from http header or the default value "defaultName" is used
  contentType: "...", //content type of the uploaded file;
                      //if not set it is obtained from http header or the default value "application/octet-stream" is used
  data: ... //binary data; required
};
```
#### Validation schema
```javascript
shape({
  code: code(),
  name: uu5String(255),
  description: uu5String(4000),
  versionName: uu5String(255),
  filename: string(255), 
  contentType: string(256),
  data: binary().isRequired()
})
```
#### Output
```javascript
{
  id: "...", //generated unique code
  awid: "...", //app module id - unique code specified externally
  sys: {},
  name: "...", //user name of binary; It is uu5String limited to 255 characters
  code: "...", //identifier of the binary (all versions of binary have same code)
  description: "...", //user description of binary
  versionName: "...", //user name of binary version
  filename: "..." //name of the uploaded file
  contentType: "...", //content type of the uploaded file
  uuAppErrorMap: {} //uuApp standard errorMap
};
```

resources.name: uu-app-binarystore/getBinaryData
resources.description:
#### uuCmd documentation
https://uuapp.plus4u.net/uu-bookkit-maing01/34df77ebe0a04adda6dcd62d32c4f513/book/page?code=getBinaryData_00

#### Input
```javascript
{ 
  code: "...", //identifier of the binary (all versions of binary have same code)
  contentDisposition: "..." //style of returned binary data; possible values: ["inline", "attachment"]; default value "attachment"  
};
```
#### Validation schema
```javascript
shape({
  code: code().isRequired(),
  contentDisposition: oneOf(["inline","attachment"])
})
```
#### Output
 Returns a binary data stream.
